OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome showery rain and showers moving
OL,7,Feast overnight but becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly patchy, with mainly dry
OL,9,Fconditions and some cloud breaks
OL,10,Fdeveloping by daybreak. Generally
OL,11,Flight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FEarly cloud and any residual
OL,14,Fpatchy rain, soon clearing to leave a
OL,15,Fgenerally dry and bright day with
OL,16,Fsunny spells later. Temperatures
OL,17,Fslightly lower than previous days, but
OL,18,Fstill warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
