OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry and fine, just a chance
OL,7,Fof isolated thunderstorms.
OL,8,FTemperatures climbing, becoming hot
OL,9,Fand humid. Mostly light winds.
